    <h1>Intro for eZ Publish 4.x/3.x developers</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>This document is not meant to be a comprehensive guide to either=
 Symfony 2 or eZ Publish 5, but to give an overview of how common concepts =
and tasks used in older versions translate into the new one.</p>
